title: DDFP 121: A.J. Hawk & Troy Aikman
itunes:title: DDFP 121: A.J. Hawk & Troy Aikman
description:
Shek & Rank get you - and themselves - ready for the terrific quartet of Divisional Round games with the help of Green Bay Packers LB AJ Hawk & Fox analyst Troy Aikman; plus, the guys discuss some of the other headlines in a big sports week like RG3’s knee injury and the baseball hall of fame.
